trans-unit.source: Provides qualifying information to a callback method when a <see cref="E:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject.ObjectChanged" /> event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona información a un método de callback para distinguir cuándo se produce un evento <see cref="E:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject.ObjectChanged" />.

trans-unit.source: PeerObjects are run-time data items associated with an application, such as certificates, pictures, avatars, or specific descriptions.
trans-unit.target: Los PeerObjects son elementos de datos de tiempo de ejecución asociada a una aplicación, como certificados, imágenes, avatares o descripciones específicas.

trans-unit.source: They may also be referred to as a host peer's registered applications, objects and presence information.
trans-unit.target: Puede también se conoce como aplicaciones registradas, objetos e información de presencia de host del mismo nivel.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject> is changed, an event is raised.
trans-unit.target: Cuando un <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject> es cambia, se genera un evento.

trans-unit.source: Calling this method requires a <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState> of <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState.Unrestricted>.
trans-unit.target: Llamar a este método requiere un <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState> de <xref:System.Security.Permissions.PermissionState.Unrestricted>.

trans-unit.source: This state is created when the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration> session begins.
trans-unit.target: Este estado se crea cuando el <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration> inicia sesión.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType" /> that specifies the type of change that has occurred to a <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.Peer" /> or <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor de <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType" /> que especifica el tipo de cambio que se ha producido en <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.Peer" /> o <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" />.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType" /> that specifies the type of change that has occurred.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerChangeType" /> que especifica el tipo de cambio que se ha producido.

trans-unit.source: Unless specified, the default value for this property is `null`.
trans-unit.target: A menos que se especifique, el valor predeterminado de esta propiedad es `null`.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> associated with the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> for which object information has changed.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> asociado al <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> en el que ha cambiado la información de objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> associated with the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> on which <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" /> information has changed.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact" /> asociado al <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> en el que ha cambiado la información de <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" />.

trans-unit.source: If the endpoint is not associated with a contact, <see langword="null" /> is returned.
trans-unit.target: Si el extremo no está asociado a un contacto, se devuelve <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> for which object information has changed.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> en el que ha cambiado la información de objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> on which <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" /> information has changed.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerEndPoint" /> en el que ha cambiado la información de <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" />.

trans-unit.source: Unless specified, the default value for this property is `null`.
trans-unit.target: A menos que se especifique, el valor predeterminado de esta propiedad es `null`.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" /> that has been added, deleted or updated.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" /> que se ha agregado, eliminado o actualizado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" /> that has been added, deleted, or updated.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerObject" /> que se ha agregado, eliminado o actualizado.

trans-unit.source: Unless specified, the default value for this property is `null`.
trans-unit.target: A menos que se especifique, el valor predeterminado de esta propiedad es `null`.
